│ The function `planContainsAdditionalSimplifications` checks if the VPlan contains extra │
│ simplifications not accounted for in the legacy cost model. It does this by comparing   │
│ the instructions in the loop with those in the VPlan. If there are instructions in the  │
│ loop that are not part of the VPlan or are skipped for cost computation, it concludes   │
